    "causal_summary": "OpenCode CLI orchestrator enabling external AI runtimes (Claude Code, Codex, Copilot, raw shell) and in-OpenCode operators to invoke opencode run for full plugin, skill, and MCP runtime dispatch, plus parallel detached sessions for ablation, worker farms, and cross-AI handback. Defaults to the direct deepseek provider (model deepseek-v4-pro, variant high). It matters because it is the only one-shot dispatch path that loads every project plugin, skill, MCP server, and the Spec Kit Memory database; the four sibling cli-* skills only dispatch raw models without project context.",
